This was a nice comeback from Binto's previous doujins release not Bitch Gyaru because that was amazing, I meant this Papa Katsu and as much I care Binto is still consistent despite making some underwhelming stuff like Papa Katsu! and that genderbend one, honestly my problem with his stuff most of the time (that can also be found here) is that it feels dull at certain pages and the way he positions stuff feel plain an example would be this https://nhentai.net/g/246879/8/ I feel like it isn't intense enough, Binto could've made it a close up shot zooming deep into the ass to add more impact and panelling could've been done better as well though some pages are really nice though which is what I like about Binto he draws such detailed ass like in page 7 I also like the the way he shades and lights stuff the drawings have this shiny & bouncy feeling to them, overall I'd give this a strong 7/10 it would've been better if Binto made some panels look better, also page 13 is HOT tbh.
